cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

This paper deals with natural language processing and computer vision, which are the main topics of cs.CL and cs.CV respectively. The use of neural language models and distributional semantics also suggests a focus on machine learning, which is covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. Finally, the evaluation of the approach on large datasets suggests a potential relevance to information retrieval, which falls under cs.IR.
